56:18.000 --> 56:31.000
It is clear that this is the format of profit, because bankruptcy is expressed in debt, so the profit before the payment of taxes is taken.

56:32.000 --> 56:37.000
The second component for comparison is the debt load on the profit.

56:37.000 --> 56:45.000
The amount of the main debt plus the interest for this debt within one year.

56:45.000 --> 56:51.000
