56:51.000 --> 56:56.000
This term is often used in textbooks.

56:56.000 --> 57:05.000
The condition of bankruptcy for any year is as follows.

57:05.000 --> 57:12.000
The profit before the payment of interest and taxes is less than the debt load on the profit.

57:12.000 --> 57:15.000
This is the condition of bankruptcy.

57:15.000 --> 57:20.000
If the company enters this stage, the debt load must be reduced immediately.

57:21.000 --> 57:31.000
It is clear that the concept of bankruptcy, as the most clear from the point of view of business,

57:31.000 --> 57:37.000
opens the method of optimization of the structure of capital,

57:37.000 --> 57:46.000
the means of operational profit, as the most understandable to the practicing financiers.

57:47.000 --> 57:52.000
The method has two assumptions.

57:52.000 --> 57:57.000
